CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season"
TitMainTitle: Men and women gathered at picnic table with soft drink, liquor, and beer bottles, with cooler in grass in foreground, at Lovuola's Farm for Junior Mothers night picnic during FROGS week
